                    [6a4b8aa0d2d76] => Array
                        (
                            [field_6a4b89c2caef8] => Do you provide high-risk pregnancy care?
                            [field_6a4b89cecaef9] => Yes. Our expert obstetricians and fetal medicine specialists provide advanced care and monitoring for high-risk pregnancies to ensure the best outcomes for both mother and baby.
                        )

                    [6a4b8ab4d2d77] => Array
                        (
                            [field_6a4b89c2caef8] => Does the hospital have NICU and PICU facilities?
                            [field_6a4b89cecaef9] => Yes. We have state-of-the-art Neonatal Intensive Care Unit (NICU) and Pediatric Intensive Care Unit (PICU) facilities for newborns and children requiring specialized critical care.
                        )

                    [6a4b8ac9d2d78] => Array
                        (
                            [field_6a4b89c2caef8] => What pediatric specialties are available?
                            [field_6a4b89cecaef9] => We offer pediatric super-specialty services including Pediatric Cardiology, Nephrology, Neurology, Endocrinology, Gastroenterology, Hemato Oncology, Pulmonology, and Pediatric Surgery.
                        )

                    [6a4b8adcd2d79] => Array
                        (
                            [field_6a4b89c2caef8] => Do you provide vaccination services for children?
                            [field_6a4b89cecaef9] => Yes. We offer comprehensive immunization and vaccination programs as per national and international guidelines.
